Our Android application only requests access to the public downloads folder on your device.
We respect your privacy and we do not collect, use, or disclose any personal information about you.
The access to the public downloads folder is solely used to enable you to download and save files from our application.

We do not share your personal information with any third party, except as required by law.
We do not use cookies or any other tracking technology to collect information about your usage of our application.

We take reasonable measures to protect your personal information from unauthorized access, use, or disclosure.
However, please be aware that no security measures are perfect and we cannot guarantee the security of your personal information.

By using our application, you consent to our privacy policy.
If you have any questions or concerns about our privacy policy or the use of your personal information, please contact us at jonas.coenen005@gmail.com.

Please note that this privacy policy may be updated from time to time.
If we make any material changes to our privacy policy, we will notify you by posting the updated policy on our website or through our application.
